---
// Features section component
---

<section id="features" class="py-24 bg-neutral-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-900 sm:text-4xl">
        强大的功能特色
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-neutral-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        从想法记录到深度分析，我们提供完整的创业想法管理解决方案
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Features grid -->
    <div class="mt-20 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <!-- Feature 1: AI Enhancement -->
      <div class="card-interactive group">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary-200 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">AI智能增强</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">
          集成Gemini AI，为您的创业想法提供深度分析、市场洞察和改进建议，让每个想法都得到专业的AI增强。
        </p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-500 space-y-1">
          <li>• 市场分析和竞争对手研究</li>
          <li>• 功能建议和产品优化</li>
          <li>• 商业模式分析</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Feature 2: PG Evaluation -->
      <div class="card-interactive group">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-secondary-100 rounded-lg mb-6 group-hover:bg-secondary-200 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-secondary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">PG评估框架</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">
          基于Paul Graham的创业评估方法，系统化评估想法的可行性、市场需求和扩展潜力。
        </p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-500 space-y-1">
          <li>• 个人问题验证</li>
          <li>• 市场需求评估</li>
          <li>• 技术可行性分析</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Feature 3: Visual Analytics -->
      <div class="card-interactive group">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-accent-100 rounded-lg mb-6 group-hover:bg-accent-200 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">可视化分析</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">
          通过Deep Well图表和雷达图，直观展示想法的用户需求强度和市场潜力，帮助您快速识别最有价值的机会。
        </p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-500 space-y-1">
          <li>• Deep Well象限图</li>
          <li>• PG评估雷达图</li>
          <li>• 趋势分析图表</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Feature 4: Smart Organization -->
      <div class="card-interactive group">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-warning-100 rounded-lg mb-6 group-hover:bg-warning-200 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-warning-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">智能组织</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">
          强大的分类、标签和搜索功能，让您轻松管理大量创业想法，快速找到需要的信息。
        </p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-500 space-y-1">
          <li>• 智能分类和标签</li>
          <li>• 高级搜索和筛选</li>
          <li>• 批量操作管理</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Feature 5: Collaboration -->
      <div class="card-interactive group">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-success-100 rounded-lg mb-6 group-hover:bg-success-200 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-success-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">团队协作</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">
          支持团队成员之间的想法分享、评论和协作，让创新成为团队的集体智慧。
        </p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-500 space-y-1">
          <li>• 想法分享和评论</li>
          <li>• 团队评估协作</li>
          <li>• 权限管理控制</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Feature 6: Progress Tracking -->
      <div class="card-interactive group">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-info-100 rounded-lg mb-6 group-hover:bg-info-200 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-info-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">进度跟踪</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">
          从想法到产品的完整生命周期管理，跟踪每个阶段的进展和里程碑。
        </p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-500 space-y-1">
          <li>• 阶段进度管理</li>
          <li>• 里程碑记录</li>
          <li>• 时间线追踪</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Bottom CTA -->
    <div class="mt-16 text-center">
      <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 mb-6">
        准备好开始管理您的创业想法了吗？
      </p>
      <a href="/dashboard" class="btn-primary btn-lg">
        免费开始使用
        <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
